          As you study his past fights, you see that Korlox has {Korlox_health} health when you only have a mere {health} health.
          The upside is that your have {damage} when Korlox only has {Korlox_damage}.
          You have {sheild} defence while Korlox has none.''')
          
    input('''In your next fight, you will have a different type of battle, being able to chose what strike your want to do.
          Through this you will be able to have more options and the battle will be more intense.''')
    
